"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:956
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Execute the chosen external script in &sheets;. &sheets; supports scripting "
"in JavaScript, Python and Ruby. Default examples of the scripts can be found "
"in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> submenu."
msgstr ""
"Izvrši željenu vanjsku skriptu u &sheets;. &sheets; podržava skriptanje u "
"JavaScript, Python i Ruby. Zadani primjeri skripti mogu se naći u "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Alati</guimenu><guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> podmeniju."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:960
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Alati</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:964
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can execute the script to export or import data in various formats, "
"save your &sheets; log into file, use <ulink url=\"https://live.gnome.org/"
"Orca\">Orca speech</ulink> for accessibility, debug Python and Ruby scripts "
"or add functions to display stock or weather condition values. You can even "
"use some <ulink url=\"http://www.r-project.org/\">R functions</ulink> "
"(<ulink url=\"http://rpy.sourceforge.net/rpy.html\">RPy module</ulink> "
"should be installed)."
msgstr ""
"Ovdje možete izvršavati skripte i izvesti ili učiteiti podatke različitih "
"formata, sačuvati vaš &sheets; upiši u dokument, koristite <ulink url="
"\"https://live.gnome.org/Orca\">Orca speech</ulink> za pristupačnost, "
"debagiranje Python i Ruby skripte ili dodajte funkcije za prikaz steka ili "
"vrijednosti vremenskih uslova. Možete koristiti čak i neke <ulink url="
"\"http://www.r-project.org/\">R funkcije</ulink> (<ulink url=\"http://rpy."
"sourceforge.net/rpy.html\">RPy module</ulink> bi trebali biti instalirani)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:968
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Script Manager...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Alati</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Organizator skripti...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:972
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Opens</action> the <guilabel>Scripts Manager</guilabel> dialog to "
"execute, load, unload, install, uninstall and get more scripts."
msgstr ""
"<action>Otvara</action><guilabel>Organizator skripti</guilabel> okvir za "
"izvršavanje, učitavanje, preuzimanje, instaliranje, deinstaliranje skripti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:977
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Function Optimizer...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Alati</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Optimizator funkcija...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:981
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Opens</action> the <guilabel>Function Optimizer</guilabel> dialog "
"where you can choose an objective function cell, optimization target "
"(<guilabel>Maximize</guilabel>, <guilabel>Minimize</guilabel> or enter the "
"<guilabel>Value</guilabel>) and a set of decision parameter cells."
msgstr ""
"<action>Otvara</action>  <guilabel>Optimizator funkcija</guilabel> okvir "
"gdje možete odabrati neku objektivnu funkcijsku ćeliju, optimizacijski cilj "
"(<guilabel>Maksimiziraj</guilabel>, <guilabel>Minimiziraj</guilabel> ili "
"unesi <guilabel>Vrijednst</guilabel>) i skup osobina ćelije."

#. Tag: title
#: commands.docbook:988
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Menu"
msgstr "Meni sa postavkama"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:992
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Toolbars Shown</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Prikaz alatnih traka</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:996
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Show or hide the toolbars: <guilabel>File</guilabel>, <guilabel>Edit</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Navigation</guilabel>, <guilabel>Font</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Format</guilabel> and <guilabel>Color/Border</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Prikaži ili sakrij alatne trake: <guilabel>Dokument</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Uredi</guilabel>, <guilabel>Navigacija</guilabel>, <guilabel>Font</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Format</guilabel> i <guilabel>Boja/Okvir</guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:1015
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Status Bar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Statusna traka</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:1019
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Show or hide the Status Bar.</action> The Status Bar shows "
"additional information for selected items and instant calculations of the "
"selected cells."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaži ili sakrij Statusnu traku.</action> Statusna traka prikazuje "
"dodatne informacije za odabrane stavke i trenutne proračune odabranih ćelija."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:1026
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tab Bar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Traka sa karticama</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:1030
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Show or hide the Tab Bar.</action> All Sheets of the current "
"Document can be accessed through the Tab Bar."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaži ili sakrij traku sa karticama.</action> Svim listovima "
"trenutnog dokumenta se može pristupiti u Traci sa karticama ."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:1036
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Podesite kratice...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:1040
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Configure the keyboard shortcuts used by &sheets;. </action> See the "
"section on <link linkend=\"configshort\">configuring shortcuts </link> for "
"more details."
msgstr ""
"<action>Podesite kratice na tastaturi korištene od strane &sheets;. </"
"action> Vidjeti odjeljak na <link linkend=\"configshort\">configuring "
"shortcuts </link> za više detalja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:1048
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Podesite alatne trake...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:1052
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Configure the toolbars.</action> The section on <link linkend="
"\"configtoolbars\">configuring toolbars</link> has more information."
msgstr ""
"<action>Podesi alatne trake.</action> Ovaj odjeljak na <link linkend="
"\"configtoolbars\">configuring toolbars</link> sadrži više informacija."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:1059
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Themes</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Teme</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:1063
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Choose the color theme for &sheets; window.</action> You can choose "
"one of the predefined color schemes or select <guimenuitem>Configuration...</"
"guimenuitem> to open <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/colors\">&systemsettings; "
"color selection module</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odaberite boju teme za &sheets; prozor.</action> Možete odabrati "
"neku od ponuđenih boja ili odabrati <guimenuitem>Podešavanja...</"
"guimenuitem> da otvorite <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/colors"
"\">&systemsettings; modul za odabir boja</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:1070
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Active Author Profile</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Aktivni profil autora</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:1074
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Configure the author profile for the current document.</action> You "
"can choose one of the profiles defined using <link linkend=\"configauthor"
"\">&sheets; configuration window</link>, <guimenuitem>Default Author "
"Profile</guimenuitem> as defined by &systemsettings; data or blank "
"<guimenuitem>Anonymous</guimenuitem> profile which can ensure your privacy."
msgstr ""
"<action>Podesite profil autora za trenutni dokument.</action> Možete "
"odabrati jedan od profila definiranih korištenjem <link linkend="
"\"configauthor\">&sheets; prozora za podešavanja</link>, <guimenuitem>Zadani "
"profil autora</guimenuitem> definiran kao &systemsettings; podaci ili prazan "
"<guimenuitem>Anoniman</guimenuitem> profil koji će osigurati privatnost."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:1082
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Notifications...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Postavke obavijesti...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:1086
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Configure &sheets; notification system.</action> There are no "
"actions that you can be notified in the current version of &sheets;."
msgstr ""
"<action>Podesi &sheets; sistem obavještenja.</action> Nema postupaka o "
"kojima možete biti obavješteni u trenutnoj verziji &sheets;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:1092
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &sheets;...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Podesi &sheets;...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:1096
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>General &sheets; configuration.</action> See the section on <link "
"linkend=\"configdialog\">&sheets; configuration</link> for more details."
msgstr ""
"<action>Opšta podešavanja &sheets;.</action> Vidjeti odjeljak na <link "
"linkend=\"configdialog\">&sheets; podešavanja</link> za više detalja."

#. Tag: title
#: commands.docbook:1106
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni za pomoć"

#. Tag: sect1
#: commands.docbook:1106
#, no-c-format
msgid "&help.menu.documentation;"
msgstr "&help.menu.documentation;"

#. Tag: title
#: commands.docbook:1113
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Right Mouse Button Menu"
msgstr "Meni u lijevoj tipki miša"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:1114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section describes the items in the pop up menu obtained by "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking on a selected cell or cells, "
"row(s) or column(s)."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj dio opisuje stavke u meniju koji se pojavi pritiskom na "
"<mousebutton>desni</mousebutton> pritisak miša u odabranoj ćeliji, redu(ima) "
"ili koloni(ma)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:1121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenuitem>Cell Format...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenuitem>Format ćelije...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:1134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Isjeci</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:1140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Put selected item(s) into the clipboard.</action> If you then do a "
"<guilabel>Paste</guilabel> the item(s) will be moved from the original "
"location to the new one."
msgstr ""
"<action>Stavlja odabrane stavke u međuspremnik.</action> Ako zatim uradite "
"<guilabel>Zalijepi</guilabel> stavke će biti pomjerene sa originalne "
"lokacije na novu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:1147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy selected item(s) into the clipboard."
msgstr "Kopira odabrane stavke u međuspremnik."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:1158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Zalijepi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1164
#, no-c-format
msgid "Paste item(s) from the clipboard to the selected cells."
msgstr "Zalijepi stavke iz međuspremnika u odabrane ćelije."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Special Paste..."
msgstr "Posebno umetanje..."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1182
#, no-c-format
msgid "Paste with Insertion"
msgstr "Zalijepi sa umetanjem"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Paste from the clipboard to the selected cell(s), moving the previous "
"cell(s) to make room."
msgstr ""
"Zalijepi iz međuspremnika u odabrane ćelije, pomjerajući prethodne ćelije da "
"napravi prostor."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1191
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Sve</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1193
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete contents of selected cell(s)."
msgstr "Brisanje sadržaja odabranih ćelija."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adjust Row &amp; Column"
msgstr "Prilagodi red &amp; kolonu"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change size of row and column to display selected cell(s) completely."
msgstr ""
"Mijenja veličinu reda i kolone da odabrane ćelije budu prikazane u "
"potpunosti."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default"
msgstr "Zadano"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1210
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set default formats for selected cell(s)."
msgstr "Postavlja zadane formate za izabrane ćelije."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1216
#, no-c-format
msgid "Area Name..."
msgstr "Ime područja..."

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:1218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Name selected area.</action> See the section <link linkend="
"\"namedareas\">Named Areas</link> for more details."
msgstr ""
"<action>Imenuj odabrano područje.</action> Vidjeti odjeljak <link linkend="
"\"namedareas\">Imenovana područja</link> za više detalja."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resize Row..."
msgstr "Promijeni veličinu reda..."

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1227
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change height of selected row."
msgstr "Promijeni visinu odabranog reda."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adjust Row"
msgstr "Prilagodi red"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1235
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change height of selected row to display cell(s) completely."
msgstr "Promijeni visinu odabranog reda da prikažete ćelije u potpunosti."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1242
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resize Column..."
msgstr "Promijeni veličinu kolone..."

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change width of selected column."
msgstr "Promijeni širinu odabrane kolone."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1250
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adjust Column"
msgstr "Prilagodi kolonu"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1252
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change width of selected column to display cell(s) completely."
msgstr "Promijeni širinu odaobrane kolone za prikaz cijelog sadržaja."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1259
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert Cells..."
msgstr "Umetni ćelije..."

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Insert new cell(s) at selected location, moving existing cell(s) to make "
"room."
msgstr ""
"Umetni nove ćelije na odabranu lokaciju, pomjerajući postojeće ćelije da se "
"napravi prostor."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1268
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete Cells..."
msgstr "Briši ćelije..."

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remove selected cell(s), moving other cell(s) to occupy the space left by "
"the removed cell(s)."
msgstr ""
"Uklanja odabrane ćelije, pomjerajući ostale ćelije da zauzmu prostor ostao "
"iza uklonjenih ćelija."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert Rows"
msgstr "Umetni redove"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1279
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert new row(s) above selected row(s)."
msgstr "Umetni nove redove iznad odabranih redova."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1286
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete Rows"
msgstr "Obriši redove"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete selected row(s)."
msgstr "Obriši odabrane redove."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1294
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide Rows"
msgstr "Sakrij redove"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1296
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hides selected row(s)."
msgstr "Sakrij odabrane redove."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Rows"
msgstr "Prikaži redove"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows selected row(s). In order to show hidden rows you need to select a "
"range of rows that includes the hidden rows."
msgstr ""
"Prikaži odabrane redove. U cilju prikaza sakrivenih redova trebate odabrati "
"opseg redova koji uključuje skrivene redove."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1312
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert Columns"
msgstr "Umetni kolone"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1314
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert new column(s) at left of selected column(s)."
msgstr "Umetnuti nove kolone lijevo od odabranih kolona."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete Columns"
msgstr "Obriši kolone"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1323
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete selected column(s)."
msgstr "Obriši odabrane kolone."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1329
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide Columns"
msgstr "Sakrij kolone"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1331
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hides selected column(s)."
msgstr "Sakrij odabrane kolone."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1337
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Columns"
msgstr "Prikaži Kolone"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows selected column(s). In order to show hidden columns you need to select "
"a range of columns that includes the hidden columns."
msgstr ""
"Prikaži odabrane kolone. U cilju prikaza sakrivenih kolona trebate odabrati "
"opseg kolona koji uključuje skrivene kolone."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1347
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comment..."
msgstr "Komentar..."

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1349
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add or modify a comment to the selected cell."
msgstr "Dodaj ili izmijeni komentar odabranih ćelija."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:1355
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selection List..."
msgstr "Lista izbora..."

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lets you select and paste text from any cell of the current selection of "
"cells into the selected cell."
msgstr ""
"Dozvoljava vam da odaberete i zalijepite tekst iz bilo koje oda trenutnog "
"dijela ćelija u odabranu ćeliju."

#. Tag: title
#: commands.docbook:1374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Shortcuts"
msgstr "Ostale kratice"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:1375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section describes those &sheets; shortcut keys used for operations that "
"do not appear in any of the menus."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj dio opisuje one &sheets; kratice korištene  za operacije koje se ne "
"pojavljuju ni u jednom od menija."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: commands.docbook:1382
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:1384
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle the display of the dockers."
msgstr "Kretanje po ekranu."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: commands.docbook:1389
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keysym>Arrow keys</keysym>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keysym>Strelice</keysym>"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1391
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the selected cell is occupied then move the cell cursor to the start or "
"end of the occupied block in the current row or column. If the selected cell "
"is not occupied then move the cell cursor to the start or end of the block "
"of unoccupied cells in the current row or column."
msgstr ""
"Ako je odabrana ćelija zauzeta pomjerite pokazivač od početka do kraja "
"zauzetog bloka u trenutnom redu ili koloni. Ako odabrana ćelija nije zauzeta "
"onda pomjerite pokazivač na ćeliju na početak ili na kraj bloka nezauzetih "
"ćelija u trenutnom redu ili koloni."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: commands.docbook:1401
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Shift;<keysym>Arrow keys</keysym>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Shift;<keysym>Strelice</keysym>"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:1403
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the selected cell is occupied then select all occupied cells to the start "
"or end of that block of occupied cells in the current row or column. If the "
"selected cell is not occupied then select all unoccupied cells to the start "
"or end of that block of unoccupied cells in the current row or column."
msgstr ""
"Ako je odabrana ćelija zauzeta onda odaberite sve zauzete ćelije od početka "
"do kraja bloka zauzetih ćelija u trenutnom redu ili koloni. Ako odabrana "
"ćelija nije zauzeta odaberite sve nezauzete ćelije od početka do kraja tog "
"bloka nezauzetih ćelija u trenutnom redu ili koloni."

